sevenbridges.models.compound package¶

Submodules¶

sevenbridges.models.compound.batch_by module¶

sevenbridges.models.compound.batch_by.BatchBy[source]¶

Batch by tells the API what is the criteria for batching. It can be either item or criteria.

sevenbridges.models.compound.batch_group module¶

sevenbridges.models.compound.batch_group.BatchGroup[source]¶

Batch group for a batch task. Represents the group that is assigned to the child task from the batching criteria that was used when the task was started.

sevenbridges.models.compound.download_info module¶

sevenbridges.models.compound.download_info.DownloadInfo[source]¶

Download info resource contains download url for the file.

sevenbridges.models.compound.execution_status module¶

sevenbridges.models.compound.execution_status.ExecutionStatus[source]¶

Task execution status resource. Contains information about the number of completed task steps, total number of task steps and current execution message. In case of a batch task it also contains the number of queued, running, completed, failed and aborted tasks.

sevenbridges.models.compound.file_origin module¶

sevenbridges.models.compound.file_origin.FileOrigin[source]¶

File origin resource contains information about origin of a file. Among others it contains information about the task if the file was produced during executions of a analysis.

sevenbridges.models.compound.input module¶

sevenbridges.models.compound.input.Input[source]¶

Task input wrapper.

sevenbridges.models.compound.invoice_period module¶

sevenbridges.models.compound.invoice_period.InvoicePeriod[source]¶

Invoice period resource contains datetime information about the invoice. It has from and to fields which represent the interval period for this invoice.

sevenbridges.models.compound.job module¶

sevenbridges.models.compound.job.Job[source]¶

Job resource contains information for a single executed node in the analysis.

sevenbridges.models.compound.job_instance module¶

sevenbridges.models.compound.job_instance.Instance[source]¶

Instance resource contains information regarding the instance on which the job was executed.

sevenbridges.models.compound.job_log module¶

sevenbridges.models.compound.job_log.Log[source]¶

Logs resource contains a url towards a file that contains execution logs for the job that executed.

sevenbridges.models.compound.metadata module¶

sevenbridges.models.compound.metadata.Metadata[source]¶

File metadata resource.

sevenbridges.models.compound.output module¶

sevenbridges.models.compound.output.Output[source]¶

Task Output

sevenbridges.models.compound.permissions module¶

sevenbridges.models.compound.permissions.Permissions[source]¶

Permissions resource contains member permissions in regards to the project.

sevenbridges.models.compound.price module¶

sevenbridges.models.compound.price.Price[source]¶

Price resource contains an information regarding the currency and the monet value of a certain resource.

sevenbridges.models.compound.project_breakdown module¶

sevenbridges.models.compound.project_breakdown.ProjectBreakdown[source]¶

Project breakdown resource contains information regarding billing group project breakdown costs.

sevenbridges.models.compound.task_breakdown module¶

sevenbridges.models.compound.task_breakdown.TaskBreakdown[source]¶

Task breakdown resource contains information regarding billing group analysis breakdown costs.
